  ('0f341f67-5412-4f52-86d9-1326290e6a44', 'What does aging means.', 'In Priority scheduling, when the processes wait for long time, their priority number is increased so that allocation of CPU to them is possible', 'In FCFS, when the processes wait for long time are given authority to allocate CPU to them selves', 'In SJG, when the processes wait for long time are given authority to allocate CPU to them selves', 'Both A and C', NULL, true),
